reviews.title: Could not see through the eyes, and smelled horrid.
reviews.name: jpf
reviews.review: When I received this mask for Halloween, I was excited because of how good it looked in hand. The color on it is very bright and vibrant, but there are too many issues to look past. For starters, the eye holes were in the complete wrong spot on my face, leaving my eyes staring at the inside of the mask. Second, they were too small to see through. Even when I did align myself correctly (by adjusting my positioning in the mask, which made it uncomfortable), I could not see through the tiny holes. I contemplated cutting my own with scissors, but did not want to ruin the product in the case of a return (which I did end up doing). Lastly, it smelled awful. There was this chemical scent that the mask radiated which I could not get over. From the outside, it was fine, but I was overwhelmed with this horrible aurora that made it hard to keep the mask on. Overall, the inside of the mask was designed poorly with the eye holes and its horrible smell, but the outside of it was fine. If this was needed as a decoration, I'm sure it'd be fine.
